headline: 2 Dividend Stocks to Double Up on Right Now
summary: When volatility hits the stock market, there's nothing like owning a portfolio of strong companies that pay consistent dividends every quarter.  The following stocks have an impressive record of paying dividends to shareholders.  Higher interest rates have weighed on the housing market the past few years, but the leading home improvement retailer continues to deliver solid returns.
